    "Gastro soleus 3.",
    "Iliotibial band 14 3 repetitions Â10 sets with 30-sec hold 3 days/week Outcome measure Primary outcome",
    "A unidimensional tool used to evaluate pain intensity, providing individuals with a means to assess their level of discomfort.",
    "Scores range from 0 (no pain) to 10 (severe pain) on a ten-point numerical scale.",
